        <updateDate>2020-01-06T14:50:28Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Renewable Energy Transferability Act</b></p> <p>This bill allows tax credits for renewable energy to be transferred to project partners. The bill applies to the tax credits for (1) renewable electricity production, (2) investments in renewable energy property, and (3) carbon oxide sequestration. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
